The Eastern Cape has recorded the highest number of deaths this summer, where 17 young men have died. JOHANNESBURG - The initiation season death toll for this month alone has risen to 23.The Department Of Cooperative Governance And Traditional Affairs says it s concerned by the loss of life.The Eastern Cape has recorded the highest number of deaths this summer, where 17 young men have died.The department s Legadima Leso says: Most these deaths occur in illegal initiation schools. The community knows about these schools. Why can t we work together to notify authorities about these schools? (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)